        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Community Lender Exam Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to increase the asset&nbsp;limit below which&nbsp;certain depository institutions&nbsp;are eligible for an 18-month, instead of a 12-month, examination cycle. </p>]]></text>
